What you need to know:

We at BBI, therefore, said that we need to bake a bigger cake that will remove the scarcity that makes people unable to move away from competition for resources often expressed as historical land injustices.Constitutions are about negotiating and balancing. Tearing up the document into single issues removes that balancing and puts minorities at risk of not having any of their interests taken care of because they will never have the numbers to carry those through as independent issues.